"```sql\nSELECT c.Currency\nFROM transactions_1k t\nJOIN customers c ON t.CustomerID = c.CustomerID\nWHERE t.Date = '2012-08-24' AND t.Time = '16:25:00';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the currency used by the customer who made a transaction at 16:25:00 on 2012-08-24. It joins the `transactions_1k` table with the `customers` table using the `CustomerID` as the foreign key to access the `Currency` information."